games.comment: Pierre Thomas and Reggie Bush combining for 103 yards on 24 attempts? No sacks by Gaines Adams also hurt.

Pierre Thomas outgained him; he managed 22 yards on just 4 attempts, but he also caught 7 passes for 67 receiving yards.    As for the Eagles, they gave themselves no chance by murdering themselves with countless errors. They looked great on the opening drive, establishing a quick 7-0 lead, but they imploded after that.
